author: hawkeye
msg: Fixes for Jira defect AXISCPP-167.
Allow the use of a properties file to specify a subset of tests to run, rather than running all tests and always having half the tests fail because the service is not available.
Also support for the automation of handler tests has been included.
Done by Andrew Perry, but he's still awainting access to the Axiscpp project.
